Bug ID:015
Title: 15.You can reserve without a  correct Name.
Description: Your Name is required for making a reservation but you can put an invalid Name.

Steps to Reproduce:
Step 1: Open browser and go to (https://lzcbvwog.acmebooking.com/).
Step 2: Log into your account.
Step 3: Click on Locations in the navbar.
Step 4 : Select your location.
Step 5 : Select a month.
Step 6 : Reserve a date.
Step 7 : Enter invalid Name.
Step 8 : Enter an valid Email.
Step 9 : Upload a file.
Step 10 : Press the reserve button.
Step 11 : Affirm you get the "Your reservation has been made successfully" message.



Expected Result:
When making a reservation all data you enter (name,email) should be correct in order to make a reservation.
Actual Result:
When you enter an invalid name you are still able to make a reservation.

Severity:
High  

Priority:
High

Additional Information:
Even if Both Name and Email are invalid together , you can still make a reservation

Environment:
Browser: Brave 1.70.119, Mozilla Firefox 130.0.1 (64-bit)
Operating System: Windows 10, Windows 11
Device: Desktop PC
Network:Ethernet
